            provide them with the xml, csv or jason format they require:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>XML Format: <a
                        href="{{ path('listingByDealerUsername', {'dealerid': username, '_format': 'xml'}) }}">{{ url('homepage') |trim ('/') }}{{ path('listingByDealerUsername', {'dealerid': username, '_format': 'xml'}) }}</a>
